OOC: Yan, are both combined jets (or is only one o them 
combined?) cloaked?


-Rippersnapper---

Rippersnapper transforms, parts of his body gashed and smashed 
from Galaxor's sword. "Rippersnapper can't see flying enemy!" he 
exclaims, and pulls out his gun, looking for a target.

> Sinnertwin bounds out of the line of fire, further away from all the

> a ball of searing flame towards the passing jets.
